712
00:50:22,853 --> 00:50:28,358
Rawls says it's Burrell's numbers game. Says
if I unleash him, all that bullshit goes south.

713
00:50:28,442 --> 00:50:33,113
A return of high-end police work
and it'll be the dawning of a new day.

714
00:50:33,322 --> 00:50:35,865
- Rawls said that?
- Yeah.

715
00:50:35,950 --> 00:50:40,286
Says he's just following orders,
being a good soldier.

716
00:50:40,371 --> 00:50:42,414
What do you say?

717
00:50:43,541 --> 00:50:48,294
Mr. Mayor, if you want to talk about
what happens in the street or in the Western,

