720
00:50:54,969 --> 00:50:56,720
I can respect that.

721
00:50:56,804 --> 00:51:01,057
I will say this though -
we did have one unit doing high-end stuff,

722
00:51:01,142 --> 00:51:04,686
Major Crimes working out
of an offsite on Clinton Street.

723
00:51:04,770 --> 00:51:07,981
"Did" is past tense. What wrecked it?

724
00:51:10,151 --> 00:51:12,736
Good question, Mr. Mayor.

725
00:51:12,820 --> 00:51:16,948
