how for real are you?

730
00:51:40,097 --> 00:51:44,434
Well, I guess we're going to
find that out together, aren't we...

731
00:51:44,518 --> 00:51:46,186
Colonel Daniels?

732
00:51:51,734 --> 00:51:53,735
What the fuck do we do?

733
00:51:55,029 --> 00:51:58,531
- I don't know.
